    Custodial History
Nancy Keiser had identified among her husband's personal effects these items specific to John H. Keiser's career at SSU. She called and obtained permission to send them to be processed and housed at UIS Archives/Special Collections. The donor placed no requirements or restrictions upon the collection.  
  
